                    00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:05,060
                    EDWARD:Dear Mother,
it's been quite some time.

                    2
                    00:00:07,860 --> 00:00:10,220
                    I am training with the Navy

                    3
                    00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:12,700
                    and will be given leave next month
to visit family.

                    4
                    00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,900
                    I think it would feel right
for us to meet.

                    5
                    00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:22,420
                    Are you able to come
to Keighley train station?

                    6
                    00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:26,299
                    I can meet you
in the waiting room there

                    7
                    00:00:26,340 --> 00:00:28,780
                    on the morning
of Monday the 10th of July.

                    